<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Accessibility - ShaktiRide</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2a6c, #fdbb2d);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  header {
    background: rgb(126, 79, 126);
    padding: 40px 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #ffcc70;
  }
  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }
  section {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  section h2 {
    color: #ffcc70;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  section p, li {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
  }
  ul {
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  /* Footer */

    body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.footer {
    background-color: lavender;
    padding: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.footer-column {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 150px;
    margin: 10px;
}

.footer h5 {
    color: black;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.footer a {
    color: black;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    margin: 5px 0;
}

.footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

.sign-up {
    background-color: lavender;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
}

.sign-up p {
    color: black;
    margin: 0;
}

.sign-up button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background-color: black;
    color: white;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 10px;
}

.sign-up button:hover {
    background-color: gray;
}

/* Extra Footer Styling */
.footer-extra {
    background-color: lavender;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
}

.social-icons {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.social-icons a {
    color: black;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin: 0 10px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
}

.social-icons a:hover {
    transform: scale(1.2);
    color: darkblue;
}

.app-buttons {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.app-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: black;
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    margin: 0 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.app-btn i {
    margin-right: 8px;
}

.app-btn:hover {
    background-color: gray;
}

.footer-bottom {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: black;
}

.footer-bottom a {
    color: black;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 8px;
}

.footer-bottom a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 600px) {
    .footer {
        flex-direction: column;
    }
    .social-icons a {
        font-size: 20px;
    }
    .app-btn {
        font-size: 12px;
        padding: 6px 10px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1><i class="fas fa-universal-access"></i> Accessibility at ShaktiRide</h1>
  <p>Making career guidance accessible to everyone, regardless of ability.</p>
</header>

<div class="container">
  <section>
    <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
    <p>At ShaktiRide, we are committed to providing an inclusive experience so that all individuals, including those with disabilities, can use our career guidance and personality development services.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. Accessibility Design Principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>High color contrast for better readability</li>
      <li>Readable fonts and adjustable text sizes</li>
      <li>Keyboard navigation support</li>
      <li>Clear and consistent layouts</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. Assistive Technology Support</h2>
    <p>Our platform is compatible with screen readers, voice control software, and other assistive technologies.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>4. Customizable Experience</h2>
    <p>Users can adjust font size, theme (light/dark mode), and interface preferences to suit their needs.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>5. Feedback & Contact</h2>
    <p>If you encounter any accessibility barriers, please contact us at <a href="mailto:accessibility@ShaktiRide.com">accessibility@ShaktiRide.com</a>. We aim to respond within 48 hours.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>6. Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>We continuously test and improve ShaktiRide to meet <strong>WCAG 2.1 Level AA</strong> guidelines, ensuring accessibility for all users.</p>
  </section>
</div>
